targets.rawSql:
SELECT
    user AS usuario,
    SUM(totalpages) AS value
FROM printlog
WHERE timecreated BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()
GROUP BY user
ORDER BY value DESC
LIMIT 15;

SELECT 
    SUM(totalpages) AS total_mes_passado
FROM printlog
WHERE timecreated >= DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE() - INTERVAL 1 MONTH, '%Y-%m-01')
  AND timecreated < DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(), '%Y-%m-01');

panels.title: Total de impressões no mês anterior

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    SUM(totalpages) AS total_paginas_mes
FROM printlog
WHERE 
    YEAR(timecreated) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE())
    AND MONTH(timecreated) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE());

panels.title: Total de impressões no Mês Atual
Total de impressões nos Últimos 7 dias

targets.rawSql:
SELECT SUM(totalpages) AS total_ontem
FROM printlog
WHERE timecreated >= CURDATE() - INTERVAL 1 DAY
  AND timecreated < CURDATE();

SELECT SUM(totalpages) AS total_hoje
FROM printlog
WHERE timecreated >= CURDATE()
  AND timecreated < CURDATE() + INTERVAL 1 DAY;

SELECT 
    DATE(timecreated) AS time,
    SUM(totalpages) AS total_paginas
FROM printlog
WHERE timecreated BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()
GROUP BY DATE(timecreated)
ORDER BY time ASC;

SELECT
    -- chave técnica para ordenar corretamente
    DATE_FORMAT(timecreated, '%Y-%m')        AS ano_mes,
    -- rótulo legível para o eixo / legenda
    DATE_FORMAT(timecreated, '%M %Y')       AS mes,
    SUM(totalpages)                         AS total_paginas
FROM printlog
WHERE timecreated >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 12 MONTH)
GROUP BY ano_mes, mes
ORDER BY ano_mes;

SELECT 
    DATE(timecreated) AS dia,
    SUM(totalpages) AS total_paginas
FROM printlog
WHERE timecreated >= CURDATE() - INTERVAL 30 DAY
GROUP BY DATE(timecreated)
ORDER BY dia ASC;

SELECT 
    jobid AS trabalho,
    DATE_FORMAT(timecreated, '%d/%m/%Y') AS data,
    DATE_FORMAT(timecreated, '%H:%i:%s') AS hora,
    client AS estacao,
    user AS usuario,
    printer AS impressora,
    filename AS arquivo,
    jobbytes AS tamanho,
    pagecount AS paginas,
    totalpages AS total
FROM printlog
ORDER BY timecreated DESC
LIMIT 500;
